Akpene Diata Hoggar bụ onye ọchụnta ego nke Ghana, onye na-ede blọgụ, onye na-elekọta mmadụ na onye nlereanya
Na 2018, ọ nọchitere anya mpaghara Brong-Ahafo na asọmpi Miss Universe Ghana wee merie, nke a nyere ya ohere ịnọchite anya Ghana n'otu asọmpi ahụ na ọkwa mba ụwa na Bangkok, Thailand
A mụrụ Akpene ma zụlite ya na Akatsi na mpaghara Volta nke Ghana
Ọ gara mahadum Ashesi ebe ọ gụrụ Management Information System
Tupu ya emeri asọmpi Miss Universe Ghana, ọ sonyere na-asọmpi nke Model Face nke Ghana
Ya na onye otu ya Setor Nyendu mebere Creatives Anonymous Gh, ntuziaka ọrụ okike maka ndị ntorobịa Africa
Ọ bụ onye ndụmọdụ tọrọ ntọala Sundiata Studios, ụlọ ọrụ dijitalụ na-egosiputa ihe gbasara ibi ndụ
Akpene eguzobela Peer Relief, atụmatụ gbadoro ụkwụ na ntorobịa nke na-achọ iweta mmata ahụike uche n'ihu ọha nakwa na nlebara anya obodo
Akpene bụkwa onye na-ede blọgụ njem na ụdị ndụ
Akpene agaala ọtụtụ ihe ngosi nke obodo na mba ụwa dị ka ihe nlereanya gụnyere Fashion for Peace Fashion Show na Paris Peace Forum 2018
Akpene kwenyere n'ịkwalite ọgbọ ụmụ agbọghọ na-esote n'Africa, ọzọ kwa ahụmahụ ya dị ka nwanyị na teknụzụ ozi edugawo ya n'ọrụ ọhụrụ ya nke a na-akpọ DSKVRD (Discover Yourself, Discover Your Purpose)
Mmemme ahụ na-agba ụmụ agbọghọ nọ n'obodo ndị na-enweghị ihe ọ bụla ume ka ha malite ịchọpụta onwe ha site na imepụta ihe, ịkọ akụkọ na nka dijitalụ
